HEADWORD: Parliamentarian
<hw>Par`lia*men*ta"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to Parliament.</def> <rj><au>Wood.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
